      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# 0.4.1\r\n\r\nThis release is focused on covering workflows for files that are placed in the root directory `/`\r\n\r\n## Enhancements\r\n- When you select `/` for FolderLocation and `/` for Existing Symbol you will be able to move files from the root to whatever directory you need\r\n- Added Notification when you are trying to move into directory that doesn't exists\r\n\r\n## Fixed\r\n- When you select `/` root directory it will display all files from the root\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Quick example of usage here: \r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/asd\" target=\"blank\"><img align=\"center\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rahuldkjain/github-profile-readme-generator/master/src/images/icons/Social/youtube.svg\" alt=\"asd\" height=\"30\" width=\"40\" /></a>👇\r\n[![Bulk Rename 0.4.1](https://img.youtube.com/vi/KN2pS-V2QqQ/0.jpg)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KN2pS-V2QqQ)",
