      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# RegExp search release\r\n\r\nThis release contains a new tab `Search By RegExp`\r\n\r\n## Search By RegExp\r\nUsage of Search By RegExp\r\nYou have two fields, RegExp pattern, and RegExp Flags\r\n\r\nRegExp pattern will be wrapped into `/ /`\r\n\r\n## Supported flags:\r\n\r\n- **g** - global\r\n- **i** - ignore case\r\n- **m** - multiline anchors\r\n- **s** - dot matches all (aka singleline) - works even when not natively supported\r\n- **u** - unicode (ES6)\r\n- **y** - sticky (Firefox 3+, ES6)\r\n- **n** - explicit capture\r\n- **x** - free-spacing and line comments (aka extended)\r\n- **A** - astral (requires the Unicode Base addon)\r\n\r\nThis release is opening the door for much more improvements that going to be introduced in the following versions!\r\n\r\n---\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11524061/190890038-517d9cf3-5fa0-4990-a172-91a9881bb45f.png)\r\n",
